   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Ptolemaios, a Macedonian of the company of Metrophanes of the Second Hipparchy, holder of seventy arouras, to Demetrios, an aide of the Second Hipparchy, holder of sixty arouras, greetings. I have received from you the rent (in kind) of the fourth year for (the kleros) which I leased to you in the presence of the registrars, together with what you measured out on my behalf to the royal treasury for the fourth year. Farewell. The 5th year, Pauni 23."</ab>
         </div>
